  "text": "It is important to note that [CITATION_1] renders more than 2 million synthetic images, which is approximately 50 times larger than the original Pascal 3D+ dataset. These additional images are particularly useful for deep learning methods. Therefore, we suspect that using a large of amount of similar synthesized data could improve the accuracy of the method presented here. We leave this as a potential future work. We also provide qualitative results on test images from Pascal 3D+ in Fig. 4 .",
